node.text:
The @dear.fathers podcast just dropped EP.10 and I’m the featured guest this week. Thank you to the founders Jesse Alex and Matthew Kirby for welcoming me on the platform. 
___
Fatherhood has been a powerful opportunity for me to learn, improve, and grow in life. I’m thankful for this time that my son and I get to share together daily. 
___
On this episode we talked about everything from fatherhood, my relationship with my father and stepfather, my latest book “Hope For Love,” my top TV dads, and more. To listen to this season finale episode of @dear.fathers please click the link in my profile above. 
___
#TheMissingPiece
#HopeForLove

I’m always an advocate for the importance of self-care and I commend @ScotchPorter for stepping it up and introducing products that include healthy ingredients to help with my daily grooming needs. 
___
Here’s a quick video of me using the Beard Balm and Beard Serum. I love how they keep my beard feeling smooth, smelling good, and healthy. 
___
#PullUpOnSP products will be available in select @Target locations this month. For more information visit ScotchPorter.com

node.text:
Chapter 8 - “The Value of Consistency” 
___
I watched this today and began reflecting on the power of community, purpose driven effort, and love. 
I was 26, fresh out of the Navy, and blessed to have many people support my vision with the #ThousandKingsWalk. 
We gave out $10,000 in scholarships to some incredible young men. 
Stay tuned for what’s coming next...
___
#TBT #TheMissingPiece
